high_descs: Grab the potato out of the sink
Chill the potato in the fridge
Grab the potato and head to the trash can
Put the potato in the trash
anns.task_desc: Chill the potato and put it in the trash

high_descs: Turn around and walk toward the stove. Turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the potato in the sink.
Turn right and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the potato inside the refrigerator and let it get cold, then take it out.
Move to your right to the trash can in the corner next to the refrigerator.
Put the potato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato in the trash can next to the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn around and take a small step to your left then walk to the counter then turn right.
Pick up the potato that's in front of you in the sink.
Turn right and walk to the fridge that's on your left then turn left to face it.
Chill the potato in the fridge then take it back out and close the door.
Take a step to your right to face the black garbage.
Put the potato in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato in the garbage.
